the real EC shows up when doing 'ectool version'
e.g. 'RO version:    eve_v1.1.6156-cb68604+ [...]'
while 'ectool --name=cros_fp version'
returns 'RO version:    eve_fp_v1.1.6178-a6a24d9+'.

